&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong Android software engineering experience, developing scalable production software and an excellent command of engineering fundamentals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in Kotlin and coroutines concurrency primitives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in native Android development using standard tools and frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://careers.duolingo.com/d26c1c52534fdf7f9587.svg&quot; alt=&quot;icon-star-16px&quot; width=&quot;17&quot; data-is360=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; Exceptional candidates will have...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
